 on-screen joystick that appears wherever the user drags within","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a defined hit-box. In this tutorial you’ll explore its configuration options — from","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"basic placement to lock behaviour, reading state, and custom styling.","type":"text"}],"estimatedTime":"10min","kind":"project","type":"topic","role":"project"},"doc://Sliders/tutorials/Joystick-Tutorials":{"role":"overview","kind":"overview","identifier":"doc:\/\/Sliders\/tutorials\/Joystick-Tutorials","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn how to add an on-screen joystick to your app using the built-in default"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"style and its configuration options."}],"title":"Building On-Screen Joysticks","url":"\/tutorials\/joystick-tutorials","type":"topic"},"Joystick_Basics_Step_1.png":{"type":"image","alt":"A Joystick with default styling","identifier":"Joystick_Basics_Step_1.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/Sliders\/Joystick_Basics_Step_1.png"}]},"doc://Sliders/documentation/Sliders/Joystick":{"title":"Joystick","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Joystick"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Joystick"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Sliders\/documentation\/Sliders\/Joystick","url":"\/documentation\/sliders\/joystick","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Joystick view used to control various activities such as moving a character on the screen.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The View creates a Rectangular region to act as a hitbox for drag gestures. Once a drag"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"is initiated the joystick appears on screen centered at the start location of the gesture. While","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"dragging, the thumb of the joystick is limited be within the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"radius"},{"type":"text","text":" of the sticks background circle."}],"type":"topic"}}}